I""<h3 id="house-of-brands-to-branded-house">House of brands, to branded house</h3>

<p>Amp (formerly The Commerce Company) had acquired leading Shopify products, but wanted them to unify them under the same brand language. After raising $10m, Amp engaged me create a new brand that reflected their ambition, unique culture, and could scale and adapt to the journey ahead.</p>

