    </div>
</section>

<h3 id="masks">Masks</h3>

<p>Amp needed to leverage a lot of customer content in case studies and spotlights. Working with the core angles of the logo, I created a collection of dynamic mask components in figma to make it easy to quickly created masked assets that felt on brand.</p>

