<h3 id="product-narratives">Product narratives</h3>

<p>Amp had previously relied on screenshots, but to create consistent brand assets, I created new assets and wrote new guidelines on creating them from scratch, and on brand. Creating a few collections for use in emails, landing pages, and ads.</p>

